{"tid":1127020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國關注修訂逃犯條例後　北京可引渡任何人到內地","createTime":"2019-04-26T19:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T23:08:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37a3049e98b33be6d73904c1c362300af027fc1b","tid":1127020,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T19:28:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1454781-20190426.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1454781-20190426.htm&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=e57b354d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1454781-20190426.htm&h=d3f3972d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1454781-20190426.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超在《大公報》撰文，指部分人仍然對修訂《逃犯條例》有些不了解。他說，反對人士把修訂建議定性為「中港移交安排」是不正確，強調政府提出的方案不是專為內地而設。<br />\n<br />\n對於民主派提議，在修訂加入「日落條款」，便可以先處理台灣殺人案，李家超表示，這樣做便會每次再重複現時的審議及立法程序，對拘捕行動造成很大影響及延誤。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國務院發表聲明，表示密切監察本港提出的《逃犯條例》修訂，認為修例容許特區在內地當局要求下，引渡任何人士到內地受審。"},{"pid":"a66823c6fb4f24e4bdd548d35145d4faa1de6310","tid":1127020,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T20:36:15.000Z","msg":"快d通過啦，想香港快d含家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfae9f5c2b8e12f2649816ef0c9d9e329d956cdd","tid":1127020,"uid":119864,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a66823c6fb4f24e4bdd548d35145d4faa1de6310","tid":1127020,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T20:36:15.000Z","msg":"快d通過啦，想香港快d含家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T20:52:47.000Z","msg":"咪撚戇鳩啦"},{"pid":"5233b5d30d277d1a9abe9297c4dcdad1f13d6775","tid":1127020,"uid":123859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T21:33:39.000Z","msg":"我相信會大批人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係"},{"pid":"3de175baa98c7dfc82fdc9bcda66d52f0544694d","tid":1127020,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T23:04:54.000Z","msg":"香港九成男人都返過大陸叫雞<br />\n咁係咪可以拉得上大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25058e82d9a63bb992205d3667e713eea551205b","tid":1127020,"uid":171788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfae9f5c2b8e12f2649816ef0c9d9e329d956cdd","tid":1127020,"uid":119864,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a66823c6fb4f24e4bdd548d35145d4faa1de6310","tid":1127020,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T20:36:15.000Z","msg":"快d通過啦，想香港快d含家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T20:52:47.000Z","msg":"咪撚戇鳩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T23:08:23.000Z","msg":"政府李家超班戇鳩就係一味叫你唔好驚 但又死都唔肯見美國佬解釋<br />\n咁我地只好冚家剷"}]}